#

Balsamic Glazed Pork Tenderloin

35 min
$15.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

soy

Dietary Tags:

high-proteingluten-free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

easyquicksavorymeat

Description

Juicy pork tenderloin perfectly glazed with a sweet and tangy balsamic sauce, served with a side of roasted vegetables for a wholesome meal.

Ingredients

  • pork tenderloin: 1.5 pounds
  • balsamic vinegar: 1/2 cup
  • honey: 1/4 cup
  • soy sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • vegetables (e.g., carrots, bell peppers, zucchini): 4 cups, chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • thyme: 1 teaspoon
